data.6-theming-mantine-to-match-primer#6. The:
We can override Mantine‚Äôs default theme to match Primer Design:
import { MantineProvider } from '@mantine/core';
<MantineProvider theme={{
  colors: { primary: ['#1f6feb'] },
  fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif'
}}>
  <App />
</MantineProvider>

data.font-family#Font Family:
Primary Font: Inter
Serves as the default font for headings, body text, buttons, and most UI elements.
Fallback Fonts: Arial, sans-serif
Provide a fallback for environments where the primary font is unavailable.
Monospace Font: JetBrains Mono
For code snippets.
CSS Declaration
:root {
    --font-primary: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
    --font-monospace: "JetBrainsMono";
}

data.usage-example-1#Usage Example:
h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-display);
    line-height: 1.2;
}
p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
}

data.font-weights#Font Weights:
Weights
Name	Value	Usage	Regular	400	Body text and general content.	Medium	500	Subheadings or semi-emphasis.	Bold	700	Headings and highlighted content.	
CSS Variables
:root {
    --font-weight-regular: 400;
    --font-weight-medium: 500;
    --font-weight-bold: 700;
}

data.usage-example-2#Usage Example:
h1 {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
}
p {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
}

data.text-alignment#Text Alignment:
Alignment Options
Alignment	CSS Property	Usage	Left-Aligned	text-align: left;	Default for paragraphs and headers.	Center-Aligned	text-align: center;	Titles, banners, and hero sections.	Right-Aligned	text-align: right;	Rare cases, e.g., metadata or special UI elements.	
CSS Classes
.text-left {
    text-align: left;
}
.text-center {
    text-align: center;
}
.text-right {
    text-align: right;
}
